gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 128, Lakers 94
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Lakers, 128-94. Jalen Green recorded 28 points (11-15 FG) and seven rebounds for the Rockets, while Alperen Sengun added 19 points, seven rebounds, and four assists in the victory. LeBron James tallied 18 points, six rebounds, and two assists for the Lakers. The Rockets improve to 4-3 on the season, while the Lakers fall to 3-5.
